  "texts": [
    "Thus, this component is intended to create a non-judgmental space where users can \"vent\" or talk through problems in a supportive environment.",
    "Delivery of CBT Materials and Exercises (Activities and Psychoeducation): Participants have access to a range of clinically-validated CBT content delivered through conversational interactions with the chatbot.",
    "There are two primary types of materials provided:",
    "○ Psychoeducation: Short, digestible content focused on educating users about specific psychological concepts or coping strategies (e.g., understanding cognitive distortions, building resilience).",
    "○ CBT Activities: Structured exercises inspired by CBT principles, such as thought records, behavioral activation tasks, and mindfulness practices."
